Flip it.

00:28:54.570 --> 00:28:55.571
Get another property.

00:28:55.571 --> 00:28:56.070
Sell it.

00:28:56.070 --> 00:28:56.860
Flip it.

00:28:56.860 --> 00:28:58.380
Keep going, keep
going, keep going.

