analyze the deal,

00:29:38.160 --> 00:29:40.285
you're going to analyze
the fundamentals, the area,

00:29:40.285 --> 00:29:42.520
everything that's going
on, and you're not

00:29:42.520 --> 00:29:43.880
going to bet on appreciation.

00:29:43.880 --> 00:29:47.502
