People, when we're talking,
they say, well, I live in LA,

00:45:43.340 --> 00:45:46.220
I live in San Francisco, I live
in New York, I can't invest.

00:45:46.220 --> 00:45:49.630
My belief is that within a
hundred miles of any location

00:45:49.630 --> 00:45:51.100
