00:45:59.190 --> 00:46:01.070
So I mean, there's
places nearby.

00:46:01.070 --> 00:46:02.870
That's probably what
I would recommend.

00:46:02.870 --> 00:46:04.940
And again it goes back to
the niche and strategy thing

00:46:04.940 --> 00:46:05.440
too, right?

00:46:05.440 --> 00:46:08.584
So some niches might be very
difficult in some areas.

00:46:08.584 --> 00:46:10.250
Some strategies might
be very difficult.

00:46:10.250 --> 00:46:12.930
Like, I'm not-- flipping doesn't
work real well in my area

00:46:12.930 --> 00:46:14.550
because prices are really low.

00:46:14.550 --> 00:46:15.758
They can't really shoot high.

00:46:15.758 --> 00:46:17.679
But around here people,
make millions a year

00:46:17.679 --> 00:46:18.470
on flipping houses.

00:46:18.470 --> 00:46:21.340
I'm not saying go out and flip
houses, but certain strategies,

00:46:21.340 --> 00:46:22.020
certain areas.

00:46:22.020 --> 00:46:24.950
So that would be
my thought on that.

00:46:24.950 --> 00:46:26.700
Don't know if you
have anything to add.

00:46:26.700 --> 00:46:27.200
JOSH: No.

00:46:27.200 --> 00:46:30.304
I mean ultimately,
again, you can find deals

00:46:30.304 --> 00:46:32.220
whether you're in New
York City, you're in LA,

00:46:32.220 --> 00:46:34.090
you're in San Francisco.

00:46:34.090 --> 00:46:36.920
Jordan, your property's
out in Sacramento, right?

00:46:36.920 --> 00:46:37.680
So what's that?

00:46:37.680 --> 00:46:38.942
Two, two plus hours?

00:46:38.942 --> 00:46:40.400
I mean, within a
couple hours drive

00:46:40.400 --> 00:46:44.320
you can find good deals from
any city in the country.

00:46:44.320 --> 00:46:46.440
Now that said, from my
own personal experience,

00:46:46.440 --> 00:46:49.210
the first properties I
bought were 2,000 miles away.

00:46:49.210 --> 00:46:50.660
Do not do that.

