that is, at least when
you're starting and learning

00:47:00.180 --> 00:47:02.247
about all these things,
and dealing with fires,

00:47:02.247 --> 00:47:04.580
because you're going to deal
with fires, no matter what,

00:47:04.580 --> 00:47:06.020
in the beginning.

00:47:06.020 --> 00:47:08.620
And to be able to get to
those properties, drive by,

00:47:08.620 --> 00:47:13.260
see that it's still-- hasn't
been burning down, or whatever.

00:47:13.260 --> 00:47:16.340
You want to be able to have
a quick and easy access.

00:47:16.340 --> 00:47:17.997
And other questions?

