AUDIENCE: Yes.

00:47:22.556 --> 00:47:25.538
My question is [INAUDIBLE].

00:47:32.496 --> 00:47:38.460
I buy another property to live
in that I can then convert it.

00:47:38.460 --> 00:47:42.933
But now, each time I do that,
the lenders [INAUDIBLE].

00:47:49.190 --> 00:47:52.522
Each company has to get smaller
and smaller. [INAUDIBLE].

00:47:55.380 --> 00:47:57.850
BRANDON: That's a
